guiSet.lists

Class CheckList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • guiSet.elements.GuiElement
        • guiSet.lists.CheckList

  • public class CheckList
extends GuiElement
    Clickable list of items. The items are set by the setItems(Item[]) method. Each Item is a button in the list. It has three show methods, two of them are intended to display the target list with circular o rectangular nested structure, i.e. lists that start empty and are filled by user selection of items from the sourceList.
    Author:
    jsalam
